WEBVTT

00:07.350 --> 00:09.390
(WOMAN SINGING TRADITIONAL SONG
IN ITALIAN)

00:15.290 --> 00:17.300
(WOMAN CONTINUES SINGING IN ITALIAN)

00:37.640 --> 00:39.340
Ciao.

00:42.930 --> 00:44.760
Gianni.

00:45.390 --> 00:47.060
Come with me.

00:57.080 --> 01:00.020
I see you watching me work.

01:00.450 --> 01:02.950
There is no need to hide.

01:03.950 --> 01:06.290
Let me see.

01:11.790 --> 01:14.090
FRANCA: Mm.

01:21.640 --> 01:25.610
I wanted to be a doctor
when I was your age.

01:25.620 --> 01:27.860
My father told me,

01:27.870 --> 01:30.810
"That's no job for a woman."

01:31.300 --> 01:34.980
So I became a dressmaker.

01:34.990 --> 01:38.880
At the same time, I vowed
I would never tell my children

01:38.900 --> 01:40.570
what job they should do.

01:41.190 --> 01:44.450
You must do what you love, Gianni.

01:44.460 --> 01:47.180
What you feel inside here.

01:47.190 --> 01:50.120
But it takes hard work and practice.

01:50.130 --> 01:54.820
You must learn how to sew,
how to understand the fabrics.

01:54.830 --> 01:58.860
I'll teach you, if you want.

01:58.970 --> 02:00.980
TEACHER: <i> Repeat after me.</i>

02:00.990 --> 02:03.810
<i>- Amo.</i>
- STUDENTS: <i> Amo.</i>

02:03.820 --> 02:06.850
<i>- Amas.
- Amas.</i>

02:06.860 --> 02:09.940
<i>- Amat.
- Amat.</i>

02:09.949 --> 02:13.140
<i>- Amamus.
- Amamus.</i>

02:13.150 --> 02:16.190
<i>- Amatis.
- Amatis.</i>

02:20.990 --> 02:23.480
What are you? A pervert?

02:23.490 --> 02:26.220
Not a pervert, miss, a pansy.

02:26.690 --> 02:29.890
(STUDENTS LAUGHING)

02:30.170 --> 02:31.640
Again.

02:32.600 --> 02:35.770
<i>- Amo.</i>
- STUDENTS: <i> Amo.</i>

02:35.780 --> 02:38.840
<i>- Amas.
- Amas.</i>

02:38.850 --> 02:41.970
<i>- Amamus.
- Amamus.</i>

02:41.980 --> 02:45.140
<i>- Amatis.
- Amatis.</i>

02:45.150 --> 02:48.180
<i>- Amant.
- Amant.</i>

02:48.190 --> 02:49.940
(DOOR CLOSES)

02:52.250 --> 02:54.260
(FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING)

02:57.260 --> 02:59.100
What's wrong?

02:59.540 --> 03:01.260
Nothing.

03:01.750 --> 03:05.490
Now tell me the truth.
I've no time for lies.

03:06.200 --> 03:08.590
The teacher said I was a pervert.

03:22.900 --> 03:25.530
It's beautiful.

03:30.730 --> 03:33.220
We make it for real.

03:33.230 --> 03:35.230
Yes?

03:44.710 --> 03:48.380
I can't. It's too hard.

03:52.190 --> 03:56.120
Success only comes with hard work.

03:56.130 --> 04:00.330
Many hours, many weeks, many years.

04:00.340 --> 04:02.690
And it's never easy.

04:02.700 --> 04:04.850
But that's all right.

04:05.540 --> 04:07.600
That's why it's special.

04:09.020 --> 04:11.170
Try again.

04:11.180 --> 04:13.180
♪ ♪

04:25.860 --> 04:28.060
(DOGS BARKING IN DISTANCE)

04:34.120 --> 04:35.860
MODESTO: All right, let's go.

04:35.870 --> 04:37.230
Huh, what did I say?

04:37.340 --> 04:40.370
We don't need professional movers.
We do it ourselves.

04:40.380 --> 04:43.900
Save ourselves 500 bucks.

04:43.910 --> 04:47.510
Give me a week, I can take that
500 and turn it into 10,000.

04:47.520 --> 04:48.570
(LAUGHS)

04:49.110 --> 04:51.510
Good exercise, too.

04:51.520 --> 04:53.550
Make ourselves stronger.

04:54.900 --> 04:56.440
Where's Andrew?

04:57.360 --> 04:58.880
(FAN WHIRRING)

04:58.890 --> 05:01.900
Andrew! Andrew!

05:03.550 --> 05:05.360
Andrew!

05:14.940 --> 05:16.870
Say good-bye.

05:17.710 --> 05:19.870
This is not for you.

05:28.920 --> 05:30.930
(ENGINE STARTS)

05:45.310 --> 05:47.310
(TRUCK RUMBLING, CREAKING QUIETLY)

06:05.290 --> 06:07.300
(ENGINE STOPS)

06:15.670 --> 06:17.920
Andrew. Let's go.

06:29.220 --> 06:32.430
(WHISPERING): Andrew. Come here.

06:46.190 --> 06:47.590
Where's your father?

06:47.600 --> 06:48.930
With Prince Andrew.

06:48.940 --> 06:50.940
He's being given the tour.

06:56.080 --> 06:58.110
Let's get the cushions.

06:58.120 --> 07:01.460
Go on. Help your sister.

07:06.690 --> 07:09.720
Tell me, what room is this?

07:10.830 --> 07:12.670
It's the biggest bedroom.

07:13.780 --> 07:16.180
It's the master bedroom.

07:17.360 --> 07:18.900
It's your room.

07:19.800 --> 07:21.810
You want to know why?

07:21.820 --> 07:23.690
Sit down. I'll tell you.

07:27.400 --> 07:29.700
Every morning when you wake up,

07:29.710 --> 07:32.200
and every evening when you go to sleep,

07:32.210 --> 07:34.220
I want you to remember...

07:36.290 --> 07:37.680
that you're special.

07:38.690 --> 07:40.650
And that when you feel special,

07:41.770 --> 07:43.680
success will follow.

07:47.410 --> 07:49.690
Of course, I'm gonna need this closet.

07:50.150 --> 07:51.830
(SIGHS)

07:52.160 --> 07:54.830
For all my suits.

07:56.110 --> 08:00.080
Otherwise, the room is yours.

